node.text:
Known for his iconic technicolour palette, @charlesdevilmorin threw the crowd a couture curveball by harnessing the power of M·A·C Black this season instead. Key Makeup Artist @anaellepostollec contrasted the smouldering silhouettes with bold lip looks and and pastel-slicked lids starring:

🖤Fix+ Magic Radiance
🖤Studio Radiance Face And Body Radiant Sheer Foundation
🖤Powder Kiss Lipstick in Lasting Passion and Marrakesh-mere
🖤Brow Set in Clear
🖤Shape + Shade Brow Tint
🖤Pro Palette Paintstick x 12
🖤In Extreme Dimension 3D Black Lash

node.text:
Fashion Designer Chitose Abe runs the @jeanpaulgaultier universe through the @sacaiofficial filter for the Haute Couture AW2021-22 collection. Key Makeup Artist @diane.kendal contrasts #JeanPaulGaultier’s signature pinstripe patterns with lived-in lids, boyish brows and fresh faces starring: 
🖤Studio Radiance Face And Body Radiant Sheer Foundation
🖤Studio Fix 24-Hour Smooth Wear Concealer
🖤Eye Kohl in Costa Riche, Coffee and Feline 
🖤Brow Set in Clear
🖤Eye Shadow x 9 : Semi-Sweet Times Nine
🖤Matte Lipstick in Chili
🖤Fix+ Magic Radiance

node.text:
Vivid colours, weightless fabrics and surreal silhouettes – @giambattistavalliparis serves up a lucid dream this season. Key Makeup Artist @helenevasnier helped us enter into the designer’s subconscious mind with strong yet simple looks starring warm brick red lips, fresh faces and dramatic “M·A·C Black Liners.” Bring your own look to life with:
🖤Matte Lipstick in Chili
🖤Pro Longwear Fluidline in Blacktrack
🖤In Extreme Dimension 3D Black Lash
🖤Amplified Lipstick in Blankety
🖤Studio Fix Sculpt And Shape Contour Palette

node.text:
@duranlantinkyo’s AW21 collection is a celebration of being bold and bare from face to body. Key Makeup Artist @mathiasvanhooff contrasted fresh faces with fluorescent false lashes to make the metallic textiles and negative-space silhouettes pop. Get inspired to recreate these runway looks your way with:
🖤Acrylic Paint in Primary Yellow
🖤Chomaline in Genuine Orange
🖤Pigment in Silver, Landscape Green, Rock It Yellow and Green Space
🖤Chromagraphic Liner in Primary Yellow, Landscape Green and Genuine Orange
🖤34 Boss Babe Lash, 7 Free Spirit Lash, 83 Siren Lash, 48 Show-Off Lash, 4 Idol Lash and 80 Romantic Lash
🖤Studio Finish SPF 35 Concealer
🖤Studio Fix Conceal And Correct Palette
🖤Mixing Medium
#MACBackstage
